A '''Moonshee''' is an [[Indian]] teacher of [[languages]], especially [[Hindustani]] and [[Persian]].

[[R. K. Kochhar]]<sup>[1]</sup> notes that ''"the term moonshee was used by the British for [[Muslim]] [[harkaras]]"''.

